==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Conferee
<hw>Con`fer*ee"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Referee</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who is conferred with, or
who takes part in a conference; <as>as, the <ex>conferees</ex> on the
part of the Senate</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One upon whom something is conferred.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Conference</ent>⟦br⟧
